(42, 14, 18, 23, 28, 12, 13, 'have me excused', 'Excuses and Spiritual Blindness', 'This connection highlights the theme of refusal to heed God''s call. In both passages, individuals make excuses or fail to listen, leading to spiritual consequences.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
