(42, 14, 18, 24, 5, 4, 5, 'have me excused', 'Excuses and Ignorance of God', 'This connection highlights the theme of making excuses and a lack of understanding of God''s ways. In both passages, individuals prioritize worldly concerns over spiritual obligations, reflecting a disconnect from the knowledge of the Lord.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
